msgid "The administrator has temporarily disabled the ability to create and manage trade requests for this timetable."
msgstr "Skrbnik je začasno onemogočil možnost ustvarjanja in upravljanja zahtev za menjavo za ta urnik."

msgid "What you can still do:"
